description.plain:
American video blogger and singer-songwriter Tessa Violet Williams, who is commonly known as Tessa Violet. She was born on March 20, 1990. In 2008, Tessa Violet started uploading story times, music videos, and skits on her YouTube channel.

In 2010, Tessa’s “Wizard Love – Harry Potter Music Video – Meekakitty Featuring heyhihello” went viral, giving her a much larger following. Later in 2010, she won YouTube’s $100,000 most commented video competition. In 2011, Tessa was featured in Shawna Howson’s viral video on YouTube titled “Sail”.

In 2014, Tessa released her album Maybe Trapped Mostly Troubled. The album was entirely written by Tessa Violet herself.

In 2016, she released Halloway, an EP with five songs.

In 2019, she released EP Bad Ideas, which includes 11 songs on the tracklist.
